## C. EXTENSION READING

### Recommended Articles

**Article 1: "What is Phishing? Examples and Prevention Tips"**
- Source: Cisco Cybersecurity
- URL: https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/products/security/what-is-phishing.html
- Reading time: 10-12 minutes
- Focus: Types of phishing attacks, real examples, prevention strategies

**Article 2: "Top Cybersecurity Threats in 2024"**
- Source: Forbes Technology
- URL: https://www.forbes.com/sites/forbestechcouncil/cybersecurity-threats
- Reading time: 8-10 minutes
- Focus: Emerging threats, ransomware trends, AI in cybersecurity

**Article 3: "Creating an Effective Security Policy"**
- Source: SANS Institute
- URL: https://www.sans.org/information-security-policy/
- Reading time: 15-20 minutes
- Focus: Policy structure, best practices, implementation

### Reading Questions for Self-Assessment

After reading any of the articles above, answer these questions:

1. What are the main types of cyber threats mentioned?
2. What security measures does the article recommend?
3. What modal verbs would you use to describe the recommendations? (e.g., "Companies should..." or "Organizations must...")
4. What new vocabulary did you learn from the article?
5. How does this information relate to what you learned in class?

